-- MOVES-Stanhope Capital names two to real estate advisory board
-- By Anya George Tharakan in Bangalore
-- Mon Sep 29, 2014 12:58PM EDT
-- None



Sept 29 (Reuters) - Global investment company Stanhope Capital said it appointed Bruce Bossom and William Hill to its newly created real estate advisory board.

Bossom is one of the founding partners of Orion Capital Managers LP and serves as managing director, while Hill was formerly head of property at asset management company Schroders Plc <SDR.L>.